         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Maldon ¶ Vic. ¶ 25 September 1861. ¶ Esteemed Doctor, ¶  ¶ I have had your request for support for the Heuglin expedition for several months already and hope, that it is not yet too late to add our sm...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">61.09.25c</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Florian Kupferberg</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Sammlung Perthes Archiv,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">SPA ARCH<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">PGM<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">328</seg>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               </seg>Forschungsbibliothek Gotha der Universität Erfurt.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Attachment to M to A. Petermann, 25 October 1861. MS<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>annotation<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>by Petermann: 'Erh. 21. letz. 1861' [Received 21 last (i.e. December) 1861].</p>
               </note>Maldon Sept. 25. 61</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Geehrter Herr Doctor.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Schon vor mehrere Monaten im Besitz Ihrer Aufforderung zur Unterstützung des Heuglinschen Unternehmens, hoffe ich, dass es auch jetzt noch nicht zu spät ist unsern kleinen Beitrag zu der grossen nationalen Sache zu fügen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ich habe heute an Herr Brahe eine Bankanweisung geschickt, aus deren Betrag £1.19, für die Heuglinsubscription bestimmt sind, als Ertrag einer Sammlung in dem hiesigen Verein.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Die augenblicklichen schlechten Zeitverhältnisse haben wohl unsre Sammlung geschmälert, doch da es mehr den Zweck hat unsere Sympathie zu bethätigen, als grosse Geldmittel zu liefern, so hoffe ich, dass auch unsre kleine Sammlung ihren Zweck erreicht.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Schliesslich bin ich Ihnen noch zum besten Dank verpflichtet für Ihre gefällige Antwort in jener Bitte, die Sie zu meinen Gunsten entschieden.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">Ich verbleibe hochachtungsvollst</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ihr ergebener</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr. Florian Kupferberg.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Maldon<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Vic.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">25 September 1861.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Doctor,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have had your request for support for the Heuglin expedition for several months already and hope, that it is not yet too late to add our small contribution towards this great national concern.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have today sent a bank-draft to Mr Brahe, of which the amount of £1/19.0 is meant for the Heuglin subscription, as the result of a collection in our local [German] club.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The bad conditions at the present time have probably reduced our collection, but as the purpose is more one of engaging our sympathy rather than contributing large sums of money, I hope that our small collection, too, has fulfilled this purpose.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Finally I still owe you my best thanks for your kind reply concerning that request that you decided in my favour.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Neither the request nor the reply has been found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I remain respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>your devoted</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="margin-left: 1.75in; font-size: 10pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Dr Florian Kupferberg.</p>
         </div>
